ary/95074526/the-life-of-ailred-of-rievaulx |url-access=subscription |series=Oxford Medieval Texts |publisher=[[Oxford University Press]] |location=Oxford |isbn=0 19 822256 4 |via=[[Questia]] |ref=P2 }}\n*{{cite book |editor-last=Riley |editor-first=HT |editor-link=Henry Thomas Riley |year=1853 |title=The Annals of Roger de Hoveden: Comprising the History of England and of Other Countries of Europe, From A.D. 732 to A.D. 1201 |url=https://archive.org/details/annalsofrogerdeh02hoveuoft |volume=2 |publisher=[[H. G. Bohn]] |location=London |ref=R2 }}\n*{{cite web |year=n.d. |url=http://www.bl.uk/manuscripts/FullDisplay.aspx?ref=Royal_MS_13_b_viii |title=Royal MS 13 B VIII |website=British Library |accessdate=27 July 2015 |ref=R1 }}\n*{{cite book |last=Skene |first=WF |author-link=William Forbes Skene |year=1890 |title=Celtic Scotland: A History of Ancient Alban |url=https://archive.org/details/celticscotlandhi03skenuoft |volume=3 |edition=2nd |publisher=[[David Douglas (publisher)|David Douglas]] |location=Edinburgh |ref=S7 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1841 |editor-last=Stevenson |editor-first=J |editor-link=Joseph Stevenson |title=Liber Vitae Ecclesiae Dunelmensis |url=https://archive.org/details/libervitaeeccles00durhrich |series=[[Publications of the Surtees Society]] |publisher=J.B. Nichols and Son |location=London |ol=13505351M |ref=S9 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1899 |editor-last=Storm |editor-first=G |editorlink=Gustav Storm |title=Norges Kongesagaer |url=https://archive.org/details/norgeskongesaga00bugggoog |volume=2 |publisher=I.M. Stenersens Forlag |location=Oslo |ref=S3 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1977 |origyear=1888 |editor-last=Storm |editor-first=G |editor-link=Gustav Storm |title=Islandske Annaler Indtil 1578 |hdl=10802/5009 |hdl-access=free |publisher=Norsk historisk kjeldeskrift-institutt |location=Oslo |isbn=82-7061-192-1 |ref=S2 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1871 |editor-last=Stubbs |editor-first=W |title=Chronica Magistri Rogeri de Houedene |url=https://archive.org/detail